videos.headline: Cincy's Doaks 72-yard rush sets up his 2-yard TD
videos.description: Gerrid Doaks enjoys the open field for 72 yards before being tackled within reach of the goal line, then he caps off the run with the short rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy's Doaks 72-yard rush sets up his 2-yard TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy's Ridder easily scores from 10 yards out
videos.description: Desmond Ridder takes advantage of the missed tackle and runs the ball in for the 10-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy's Ridder easily scores from 10 yards out) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder knocks out cameraman as he scores TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder rushes in the 32-yard touchdown then loses his balance and tumbles over a member of the media.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder knocks out cameraman as he scores TD) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Whyle somehow stays in bounds for TD catch
videos.description: Cincinnati's Desmond Ridder lobs the pass to Josh Whyle who gets both feet inside the lines before being knocked out of play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Whyle somehow stays in bounds for TD catch) 2020/11/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Houston's Porter waltzes into the end zone
videos.description: Kyle Porter takes the handoff and easily scores the 3-yard rushing touchdown.
